      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 347,
      "message": "E.g:\n\n   def _get_nfs_for_creation_and_deletion(self, nfs1, nfs2, action, mrpub, app_conf):\n        for x in range(len(nfs1)):\n            self.method_name(nfs1[x], action, app_conf, mrpub, nfs2)\n\n    def method_name(self, nfs1, action, app_conf, mrpub, nfs2):\n        for y in range(len(nfs2)):\n            if nfs1.nf_name == nfs2[y].nf_name:\n                self.method_name2(action, app_conf, mrpub, nfs1)\n\n    def method_name2(self, action, app_conf, mrpub, nfs1):\n        if action == 'create':\n            app_conf.subscription.create_subscription_on_nfs([nfs1], mrpub,\n                                                             app_conf)\n        if action == 'delete':\n            app_conf.subscription.delete_subscription_from_nfs([nfs1], mrpub,\n                                                               app_conf)",
